# Issue: Track Chunk Positions Through Pipeline

## Problem

Chunking pipeline loses character positions. Current workaround uses string-search which fails with duplicates/whitespace.

## Current Architecture

```python
class TextChunker(ABC):
    def chunk(self, text_segments: list[str]) -> list[str]:  # No positions!
```

## Proposed Solution

### 1. New Span Dataclass

```python
@dataclass
class TextSpan:
    text: str
    start_char: int
    end_char: int

    @classmethod
    def from_text(cls, text: str) -> "TextSpan":
        return cls(text=text, start_char=0, end_char=len(text))
```

### 2. Updated Chunker Interface

```python
class TextChunker(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def chunk(self, spans: list[TextSpan]) -> list[TextSpan]:
        """Each chunker preserves/updates positions."""
        pass
```

